''' Ramthakur''' ({{lang-bn|শ্রীশ্রী রামঠাকুর}}) (2 February 1860 – 1 May 1949) born '''Ram Chandra Chakraborty''' ({{lang-bn|রাম চন্দ্র চক্রবর্তী}}), was an Indian [[mysticism|mystic]] and [[yogi]] during 19th-century India. 

