{{Tibetan Buddhism}}
'''Taklung Tangpa''' is a [[Tibetan Buddhism|Tibetan Buddhist]] [[title]], referring back to the founding of the [[Taklung Kagyu]] 800 years ago.

It has some relationship with the biography of the 15th Talung Rinpoche.

